#: ../../docs/classes/class_bool.rst:75
msgid ""
"Cast an :ref:`int <class_int>` value to a boolean value, this method will"
" return ``true`` if called with an integer value different to 0 and "
"``false`` in other case."
msgstr ""
"将 :ref:`int <class_int>` 值转换为布尔值，如果使用不同于 ``0`` 的整数值，调用此方法，则返回 "
"``true``，否则返回 ``false``。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_bool.rst:79
